title: Bobby Talks About Leaving Radio + Bobby’s Dance Partner Sharna Burgess Stops By
itunes:title: Bobby Talks About Leaving Radio + Bobby’s Dance Partner Sharna Burgess Stops By
description:
Bobby talks about the reason he would leave radio. Also, Sharna Burgess, Bobby’s Dancing With The Stars partner, stops by to talk about winning the mirrorball and terrible partners she’s had in the past.
